OL,6,FHe added: "That was our fun place, our
OL,7,Fsanctuary. When the world was
OL,8,Fcollapsing, and everything else was
OL,9,Fgoing wrong the one sacred place and
OL,10,Fsafe place was the rink. So for that
OL,11,Fmoment or moments after it almost felt
OL,12,Flike that was taken away from us."
OL,14,FCoach Aaron Fox said: "Everyone
OL,15,Fmourned differently and some guys took
OL,16,Flonger than others and some guys
OL,17,Fpicked others up."
OL,19,FHe said it was a "tough time" but "the
OL,20,Fgroup came together the right way".
