OL,6,FThe death of Adam Johnson came after
OL,7,Fthe Steelers lost one of their own
OL,8,Fteammates, Alex Graham, before the
OL,9,Fseason began.
OL,11,FSpeaking in the documentary, Fox said
OL,12,Fhearing the news "stopped time a
OL,13,Flittle bit".
OL,15,FHe said Graham had "potential through
OL,16,Fthe roof".
